            <title>[LU-15101] sanity test_31q fails with 3 mdts</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15101</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sanity test_31q has a check to ensure that there are 3 or more mdts available.&#160; However, it runs the command &quot;lfs mkdir -i 3,1 $DIR/$tdir&quot; which will only succeed if there are 4 mdts (otherwise, the mdt with index=3 does not exist).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
